5e Solo adventure generator

Plan

1. Encounter (Combat) Generator
	-Settings
		-Difficulty
		-Goal
		-Level
		-Theme
		-Boss?
	-To Generate
		-Enemies
		-Tactics

2. Encounter (Social) Generator
	-Settings
		-Social Standings
		-Focus
		-Emotions
		-Theme
		-Participants
	-To Generate
		-Dialog
		-Options
		-Responses
		-New settings

3. Dungeon Generator
	-Settings
		-Location
		-Theme
	-To Generate
		-Layout
		-Encounters

Definitions:
	Encounter (Combat) - A single fight
	Encounter (Social) - A single conversation
	Dungeon - A location in which several encounter may take place